 For the confusion matrix below, calculate the following appraisal metrics.

	\begin{enumerate}[(i)]
		\item (1 Mark) Accuracy,
		\item (1 Mark) Recall,
		\item (1 Mark) Precision,
		\item (1 Mark) F-measure.
	\end{enumerate}


